{"tid":1758420,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"飯堂傳惡臭 爛肉滿蛆蟲","createTime":"2019-11-27T04:56:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-27T05:22:56.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f8b0c9c9d79c33958b36108f5b3508e997fbf3e9","tid":1758420,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T04:56:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191127/JGRMLKWDSQWGJR5IWJKFMZVZOY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191127%2FJGRMLKWDSQWGJR5IWJKFMZVZOY%2F&d=CdC2hxDFSK2eX8E0jz8mRAy1DEY80m5I9K8mtjxpzv8%3D&h=dcf9e098\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191127%2FJGRMLKWDSQWGJR5IWJKFMZVZOY%2F&h=fd6a4f3b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191127/JGRMLKWDSQWGJR5IWJKFMZVZOY/</a><br />\n<br />\n飯堂傳惡臭 爛肉滿蛆蟲<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191127/large/1574784456_8921.gif\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191127%2Flarge%2F1574784456_8921.gif&d=CdC2hxDFSK2eX8E0jz8mRAy1DEY80m5I9K8mtjxpzv8%3D&h=e3ad9001\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191127/large/1574784456_8921.gif</a><br />\n理大其中一個主要的飯堂發出惡臭，腐爛的食物隨處放置。黃耀興攝<br />\nA<br />\nA<br />\nA<br />\n【本報訊】理大協助小組昨日進入校園，除了搜索留守者，亦再次進入飯堂視察，發現校內衞生情況惡劣，特別是飯堂廚房，有肉類變壞發出惡臭，並生出過千條蛆蟲，觸目驚心，中人欲嘔。<br />\n<br />\n理大邵逸夫樓VA座地下的飯堂，是抗爭期間主要使用的飯堂，被警方圍困後稱為「抗爭飯堂」，由人稱「廚房佬」的一名男子為抗爭者煮食，但隨着他於上周六（23日）在救護員陪同下送院離場後，幾乎再沒有人在飯堂煮食。飯堂內堆滿食具、調味料和垃圾，變壞的生果隨處放；廚房狀況慘不忍睹，一個不銹鋼容器內的肉已經變壞，發出強烈臭味，滋生過千條蛆蟲。<br />\n食環署派人清潔<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：重提獨立檢討委員會魚目混珠<br />\n<br />\n此外，洗手盆及多個容器，混有廚餘及積水，已經不可能在該處煮食，相信留守者只能以乾糧或杯麵等充飢。另外校園內其他地方亦到處有垃圾，理大校方人員昨日清晨進入校園搜索的同時，約30名食環署工人亦戴着頭盔、口罩及眼罩等保護工具，在科學館徑進入理大封鎖區進行清潔，所有人士均由把守的警員登記資料方可進入，亦有清潔工人於科學館道清理張貼的文宣。<br />\n■記者馬耀文"},{"pid":"3c9db33d622ab78790ab180a5236163a0841a1a0","tid":1758420,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T04:58:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191127/large/1574784456_8921.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191127%2Flarge%2F1574784456_8921.gif&h=b2183c8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n理大其中一個主要的飯堂發出惡臭，腐爛的食物隨處放置。黃耀興攝"},{"pid":"0c253e27fde5bc37a6f304dac6c1bd26af3dca7a","tid":1758420,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T05:00:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QWeEy2B.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQWeEy2B.png&h=90138a27&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fgsiPAW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfgsiPAW.png&h=78ef3435&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n怕香港人善忘嘅，推行動post 啦<br />\n想聲援理大手足嘅，推行動post 啦<br />\n和理非嘅，推行動post 啦<br />\n勇武嘅，推行動 post 啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個係行動post，星期三晚，我地聚首商場，以和理非聲援理大手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1756593\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1756593</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6b0aac5f73b1357550502683e83d95cd0d4031b1","tid":1758420,"uid":142247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T05:03:41.000Z","msg":"想睇蛆蟲圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1acc91d097310fba09b37a0527b8cbeb7cb05c4","tid":1758420,"uid":294916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T05:22:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}